<P>
 6850 Topanga Canyon Blvd. Quake Aid 
</P>
<P>
 * Red Cross Service Centers 
</P>
<P>
 Caseworkers can assess disaster-caused needs, and provide vouchers for food, 
clothing, temporary housing/rental assistance, help with health/medical needs, 
urgent household items such as bedding or cookware, and some home repairs. 
Hours: 9 a.m. to 7 p.m. daily. Information: (213) 739-4543 
</P>
<P>
 Burbank 
</P>
<P>
 Machinist Union Hall 
</P>
<P>
 2600 W. Victory Blvd. 
</P>
