 * 
</P>
<P>
 * I often disagree with The Times' editorials, but on Feb. 8 you were right 
on! Serbian genocide and aggression must be halted at some point, i.e. 
Sarajevo. One caveat: Basic morality and international law clearly indicate 
that a people have a right of self-defense. The U.S. must lift the embargo and 
sanctions preventing defensive arms from reaching the legal government of 
Bosnia. 
</P>
