COTTON LEADS LONG BEACH ST. TO VICTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Freshman James Cotton had 23 points and 10 rebounds Thursday night to lead 
Long Beach State to an 88-75 Big West victory over Pacific. 
</P>
<P>
 Mike Atkinson had 20 points and eight rebounds for the 49ers (11-7, 6-5). 
Atkinson, who entered the game as the nation's leading field-goal shooter at 
69.8%, made eight of 12 from the floor. 
</P>
<P>
