<HEADLINE>
<P>
NHL ROUNDUP; FAILURE TO CONVERT PENALTY SHOT COSTS BUFFALO IN TIE WITH BOSTON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
