 Fifth-grade students at Arroyo Elementary School will hold a health fair today 
for the benefit of students, teachers and parents. 
</P>
<P>
 The fair will feature games, puppet shows and videos produced by the students 
on such topics as smoking, physical fitness and nutrition. About 90 students 
from three fifth-grade classes will have health information booths. 
