FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Education funds -- The Times on Tuesday incorrectly reported the amount of new 
education funds proposed for California's disadvantaged students in the Clinton 
Administration's 1995 budget. The increase, if approved by Congress, would 
provide between $200 million and $300 million. 
</P>
